                        <title render="doublequote" linktype="simple">The Fatal Sisters, an Ode. (From the
									Norse-tongue.) in the Orcades of Thormodus Torfaeus;
									Hafniae, 1697, Folio and also in Bartholinus</title>
                     </unittitle>
